title: BRIEF-Wangsu Science & Technology sees 9-mth net profit up 70-90 pct
text:
Oct 14 Wangsu Science & Technology Co Ltd
* Says expects 9-month net profit to rise 70-90 percent y/y at 520.0-581.2 million yuan ($81.9-$91.58 million)
